track_notes: This is one of the routes to park close to the summit. The other route is from the South and involves a LOT more climbing. The summit is located on a commercial forestry plantation and a permit needs to be obtained from the company. Please contact ZS6FY or ZS5AYC for assistance in obtaining a permit.
a fairly steep hike crossing a narrow saddle. Take enough water! 2m Kaapsehoop amateur repeater easily reachable from here.
